hadiths[76]{hadithnumber,text}:
59,aik baar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein baithey huey unse baatein kar rahe they. itney mein aik dehati aap ke paas aaya aur poochhney laga ke qiyamat Kab aaeygi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni guftgu mein masroof rahe. kuchh log (jo majlis mein they) kehney lagey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dehati ki baat suni lekin pasand nahi ki aur kuchh kehney lagey ke nahi balke aap ne uski baat suni hi nahi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni baatein poori kar chukey to main samajhta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya wo qiyamat ke barey mein poochhney wala kahan gaya us ( dehati ( ne kaha (ya Rasulullah ! ( mein maujood hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab amanat ( emaandari duniya se) uth jaey to qiyamat qaaim honey ka intizar kar. usne kaha emaandari uthney ka kya matlab hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab ( hukumat ke karobar ( naalaaiq logon ko saunp diye jayen to qiyamat ka intizar kar.
60,aik safar mein jo ham ne kya tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se peechhey reh gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se us waqt miley jab (asr ki) Namaz ka waqt aan pahuncha tha ham ( jaldi-jaldii ( wuzu kar rahe they. to paon ko khub dhoney ke badal ham yun hi sa dho rahe they. (ye haal dekh kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne buland awaz se pukara dekho eidiyon ki kharabi dozakh se honey wali hai 2 ya teen baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( yun hi buland awaz se) farmaya.
61,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya darakhton mein aik darakht aisa hai ke iske pattey nahi jhadtey aur musalman ki misal usi darakht ki si hai. bataao wo kon sa darakht hai? ye sun kar logon ka khayal jangal ke darakhton ki taraf douda. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mere dil mein aaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai. magar main apni (kam umri ki wajah se) sharm se na bola. aakhir sahaba ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi se puchha ke wo kon sa darakht hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wo khajoor ka darakht hai.
62,(eik martaba) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya darakhton mein se aik darakht aisa hai ke iske patte nahi jhadtey aur musalman ki bhi yahi misal hai batlao wo kon sa darakht hai? ye sun kar logon ke khayalat jangal ke darakhton mein chaley gaey. Abdullah ne kaha ke mere dil mein aaya ke batla dun ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai lekin) wahan bahut se buzurg maujood they us liye) mujh ko sharm aai. aakhir sahaba ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! aap hi bayan farma dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne batlaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai.
63,"aik baar ham masjid main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they, itney mein aik shakhs oont par Sawar ho kar aaya aur oont ko masjid mein bitha kar baandh diya. phir poochhney laga ( bhaiyo ( tum logon mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kon se hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt logon mein takiya lagaey baithey huey they. ham ne kaha Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye safaid rang waley buzurg hain jo takiya lagaey huey tashrif farma hain. tab wo aap se mukhaatab hua ke aey abdul-Muttalib ke farzand ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kaho main aap ki baat sun raha hun. wo bola mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh deeni baatein malum karna chahta hun aur zara sakhti se bhi poochhunga to aap apne dil mein bura na maaniyega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi jo tumhara dil chahey poochho . tab usne kaha ke main aapko aap ke rab aur agley logon ke rab tabarak w taala ki qism de kar poochhta hun kya aapko Allah ne duniya ke sab logon ki taraf rasool bana kar bheja hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan mera Allah is par gawah hai. phir usne kaha, main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Allah ki qism deta hun kya Allah ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko raat din mein panch namazein padhney ka hukm farmaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan mera Allah is par gawah hai! phir kahne laga main aapko Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun ke kya Allah ne aapko ye hukm diya hai ke saal bhar mein us mahina Ramazan ke rozey rakho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan mera Allah is par gawah hai! phir kehney laga mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun ke kya Allah ne aapko ye hukm diya hai ke aap ham mein se jo maaldaar log hain unse zakat wsool karke hamarey mohtajon mein baant diya karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan mera Allah is par gawah hai! tab wo shakhs kehney laga jo hukm Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke paas se laey hain, main un par eman laya aur main apni qaum ke logon ka jo yahan nahi aaey hain bheja hua ( tahqeeq haal ke liye) aaya hun. mera naam Zamaam-bin-Solba hai, main bani Sad bin bakar ke khandan se hun. us hadis ko) Leis ki tarah) Musa aur Ali-bin abdul-Hameed ne Sulaiman se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Sabit se, unhon-ne Anas se, unhon-ne yahi mazmoon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya hai."
64,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko apna aik khat de kar bheja aur usey ye hukm diya ke usey haakime-Bahrain ke paas ley jaey. Bahrain ke Hakim ne wo khat Kisraa (Shaahe-Iraan (ke paas bhej diya. jis waqt usne wo khat padha aur chaak kar daala ( rawi kehtey hain) aur mera khayal hai ke ibne-Musaiyab ne (iske baad) mujh se kaha ke (is waqia ko sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahal Iraan ke liye baddua ki ke wo (bhi chaak shuda khat ki tarah) tukdey-tukdey ho jaaein.
65,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kisi badshah ke naam dawate-Islam dene ke liye) aik khat likha ya likhney ka irada kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke wo baghair mehar ke khat nahi padhtey (yani be mehar ke khat ko mustanad nahi samajhtey ( tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki anguthi banwai. jis mein (Muhammad rasool Allah) khuda hua tha. aisa lagta hai jaise mein (aaj bhi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein uski safedi dekh raha hun. ( Shoba rawi hadis kehtey hain ke) maine Qatada se puchha ke ye kis ne kaha (ke ( is par) Muhammad rasool Allah) khuda hua tha? unhon-ne jawab diya, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
66,"(eik martaba ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird-gird baithey huey they ke teen aadmi wahan aaey ( unmein se) 2 Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pahunch gaey aur aik wapas chala gaya. ( rawi kehtey hain ke) phir wo donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khadey ho gaey. iske baad unmein se aik ne (jab ( majlis mein (eik jagah kuchh ( gunjaaish dekhi , to wahan baith gaya aur doosra ahal majlis ke peechhey baith gaya aur tesraa jo tha wo lot gaya. to jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apni guftgu se) farigh huey (to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se) farmaya ke kya main tumhen teen aadmiyon ke barey mein na bataaoon? to (suno) unmein se aik ne Allah se panah chahi Allah ne usey panah di aur doosrey ko sharm aai to Allah bhi us se sharmaya (ke usey bhi bakhsh diyaa) aur teesrey shakhs ne munh modaa, to Allah ne (bhi) usse munh mod liya."
67,"wo (eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tazkira kartey huey kehney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne oont par baithey huey they aur aik shakhs ne uski nakel thaam rakhi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha aaj ye kon sa din hai? ham khamosh rahe, yahan tak ke ham samjhey ke aaj ke din ka aap koi doosra naam iske naam ke ilawa tajwiz farmaaengey ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya aaj qurbani ka din nahi hai? ham ne arz kya, beshak. (iske baad) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ye kon sa mahina hai? ham (us par bhi) khamosh rahe aur ye (hii) samjhey ke us mahiney ka ( bhi) aap iske naam ke ilawa koi doosra naam tajwiz farmaaengey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya ye Zil-Hijja ka mahina nahi hai? ham ne arz kya, beshak. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, to yaqinan tumhari jaanein aur tumharey maal aur tumhari aabroo tumharey darmyan isi tarah haram hain jis tarah aaj ke din ki hurmat tumharey us mahiney aur us Shahar mein hai. to jo shakhs hazir hai usey chahiye ke ghayab ko ye (baat) pahuncha de, kyonke aisa mumkin hai ke jo shakhs yahan maujood hai wo aisey shakhs ko ye khabar pahunchaaey, jo us se zyada ( hadis ka ( yad rakhney wala ho."
68,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein nasihat farmaney ke liye kuchh din muqarrar kar diye they us dar se ke kahin ham pareshan na ho jaaein.
69,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aasani karo aur sakhti na karo aur khush karo aur nafrat na dilao ."
70,"Abdullah ( ibne-Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) har jumerat ke din logon ko waz (nasihat) sunaya kartey they. aik aadmi ne unse kaha aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main chahta hun ke tum hamein har roz waz (nasihat) sunaya karo. unhon-ne farmaya, to sun lo ke mujhey us amal se koi cheez rukawat hai to ye ke main ye baat pasand nahi karta ke kahin tum tang na ho jao aur main waz (nasihat) mein tumhari fursat ka waqt talash kya karta hun jaisa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us khayal se ke ham pareshan na ho jaaein, waz (nasihat) ke liye hamarey auqaate-fursat ka khayal rakhtey they."
71,"wo khutbe mein farma rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke jis shakhs ke sath Allah Taala bhalai ka irada karey usey Deen ki samajh inayat farma deta hai aur main to mahz taqseem karne wala hun, dene wala to Allah hi hai aur ye ummat hamesha Allah ke hukm par qaaim rahegi aur jo shakhs unki mukhalifat karega, unhein nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega , yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm (qiyamat ( aa jaey (aur ye aalim fana ho jaey) ."
72,"main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Madiney tak raha, maine (is ( aik hadis ke siwa unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi aur hadis nahi suni , wo kehtey they ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khajoor ka aik gabha laya gaya. (usey dekh kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke darakhton mein aik darakht aisa hai uski misal musalman ki tarah hai. ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ye sun kar) maine irada kya ke arz karun ke wo ( darakht ( khajoor ka hai magar chunkey main sab mein chhota tha isliye khamosh raha. ( phir ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi farmaya ke wo khajoor hai."
73,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irshad hai ke hasad sirf 2 baton mein jaaiz hai. aik to us shakhs ke barey mein jisey Allah ne daulat di ho aur wo us daulat ko raahe-haq mein kharch karne par bhi qudrat rakhta ho aur aik us shakhs ke barey mein jisey Allah ne hikmat (ki daulat ( se nawaza ho aur wo uske zariey se faisla karta ho aur) logon ko) us hikmat ki taleem deta ho.
74,"wo aur Hur-bin-Qais bin Hisn fazari Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sathi ke barey mein bahas karne lagey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke wo khizr (Alaihissalam) they. phir unke paas se Ubai-bin-Kab guzrey to Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bulaya aur kaha ke main aur mere ye rafeeq Musa (Alaihissalam) ke us sathi ke barey mein bahas kar rahe hain jis se unhon-ne mulaqat chahi thi. kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein kuchh zikr suna hai. unhon-ne kaha, haan maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai. aik din Musa Bani-Israeel ki aik jamat mein baithey huey they ke itney mein aik shakhs aaya aur us ne aap se puchha kya aap jantey hain ke) duniya mein) koi aap se bhi badh kar aalim maujood hai? Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya nahi. is par Allah Taala ne Musa (alaihissalam) ke paas wahi bheji ke yahan hamara banda khizr hai (jiska ilm tum se zyada hai) Musa (Alaihissalam) ne Allah se malum kya ke khizr (Alaihissalam) se milney ki kya sura hai? Allah Taala ne aik machhli ko unse mulaqat ki alamat qarar diya aur unse keh diya ke jab tum us machhli ko gum kar do to ( wapas ( lot jao, tab khizr se tumhari mulaqat hogi. tab Musa ( chaley aur) dariya mein machhli ki alamat talash kartey rahe. us waqt unke sathi ne kaha jab ham patthar ke paas they, kya aap ne dekha tha, main us waqt machhli ka kehna bhool gaya aur shaitan hi ne mujhey iska zikr bhulaa diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha, usi maqam ki hamein talash thi. tab wo apne nishanat qadam par (pichhley paon ( baatein kartey huey lautey ( wahan ( unhon-ne khizr (Alaihissalam) ko paya. phir unka wahi qissa hai jo Allah ne apni kitab Quran mein bayan kya hai."
75,"(eik martaba ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ( seeney se) laga liya aur dua detey huey farmaya ke ''aey Allah isey ilme-kitab ( Quran ( ata farmaiyo."""
76,"mein (eik martaba ( gadhi par Sawar ho kar chala , us zamaney mein, main baligh hone ke qareeb tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein Namaz padh rahe they aur aap ke samney diwar (ki aad) na thi, to main kuchh safon ke samney se guzra aur gadhi ko chhod diya. wo charney lagii, jabke main saf mein shamil ho gaya ( magar ( kisi ne mujhey is baat par tokaa nahi."
77,"(eik martaba ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dol se munh mein pani lekar mere chehrey par kulli farmai, aur main us waqt panch saal ka tha."
78,"wo aur Hur-bin-Qais-bin-Hisn fazari Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sathi ke barey mein jhagdey. (is doran mein) unke paas se ubaii-bin-ka'b guzrey, to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bula liya aur kaha ke main aur mere (ye ( sathi Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sathi ke barey mein bahas kar rahe hain jis se milney ki Musa (Alaihissalam) ne (Allah se) dua ki thi. kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kuchh unka zikr farmatey huey suna hai? ubaii ne kaha ke yahan! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unka haal bayan farmatey huey suna hai. aap farma rahe they ke aik baar Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ki aik jamat mein they ke itney mein aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga kya aap jantey hain ke duniya mein aap se bhi badh kar koi aalim maujood hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke nahi. tab Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) par wahi nazil ki ke yahan hamara banda khizr (ilm main tum se badh kar) hai. to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unse milney ki raah malum ki, us waqt Allah Taala ne (unse mulaqat ke liye) machhli ko nishani qarar diya aur unse keh diya ke jab tum machhli ko na paogey to lot jaana, tab tum khizr (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat kar lo gey. Musa (Alaihissalam) dariya mein machhli ke nishan ka intizar kartey rahe. tab unke khaadim ne unse kaha, kya aap ne dekha tha ke jab ham patthar ke paas they, to main ( wahan ( machhli bhool gaya aur mujhey shaitan hi ne ghaafil kar diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke ham usi ( maqam (ke to mutalashi they, tab wo apne ( qadmon ke) nishaanon par baatein kartey huey wapas lautey. ( wahan ( khizr (Alaihissalam) ko unhon-ne paya. phir unka qissa wahi hai jo Allah Taala ne apni kitab mein bayan farmaya hai."
79,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey jis ilm w hidayat ke sath bheja hai uski misal zabardast barish ki si hai jo zameen par) khub ( barsey . kuchh zameen jo saaf hoti hai wo pani ko pi leti hai aur bahut bahut sabza aur ghaas ugati hai aur kuchh zameen jo sakht hoti hai wo pani ko rok leti hai us se Allah Taala logon ko fayda pahunchata hai. wo us se sairaab hotey hain aur sairaab kartey hain. aur kuchh zameen ke kuchh khitton par pani padta hai jo bilkul chatiyal maidan hotey hain. na pani roktey hain aur na hi sabza ugaate hain. to ye us shakhs ki misal hai jo Deen mein samajh paida karey aur nafa de, usko wo cheez jiske sath mein maboos kya gaya hun. usne ilme-deen seekha aur sikhaya aur us shakhs ki misal jisne sar nahi uthaya (yani tawajjoh nahi ki) aur jo hidayat dekar mein bheja gaya hon usey qabool nahi kya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke ibne-Ishaq ne abu-Usama ki riwayat se ( قبلت الماء (ka lafz naql kya hai. ""Qa'aas"" zameen ke us tukde ko kehtey hain jis par pani chadh jaey (magar thahrey nahin) aur (safsaf) us zameen ko kehtey hain jo bilkul hamwaar ho."
80,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, alamaate-qiyamat mein se ye hai ke (diinii) ilm uth jaeyga aur jehal hi jehal zahir ho jaeyga aur (ailaaniya) sharab pi jaeygi aur zina phail jaeyga"
81,"main tum se aik aisi hadis bayan karta hun jo mere baad tum se koi nahi bayan karega, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke alamaate-qiyamat mein se ye hai ke ilm ( Deen ( kam ho jaeyga jehal zahir ho jaeyga zina kasrat se hoga. auratein badh jaengi aur mard kam ho jaengey. yahan ke 50 aurton ka nigraan sirf aik mard reh jaeyga"
82,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai ke main so raha tha (usi haalat mein) mujhey doodh ka aik piyala diya gaya. maine ( khub achi tarah) pi liya. yahan tak ke maine dekha ke taazgi mere nakhunon se nikal rahi hai. phir maine apna bacha hua ( doodh ( Umar-bin-Khattab ko de diya. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha aap ne uski kya tabeer li? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ilm.
83,"Hijjatul-wada main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke masayel malum karne ki wjah se Mina mein thahar gaey. to aik shakhs aaya aur us ne kaha ke maine be-khabri mein zabah karne se pahley sar mundaa liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ab ( zabah kar ley aur kuchh harj nahi. phir doosra aadmi aaya, usne kaha ke maine be-khabri mein rami karne se pahley qurbani kar li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ab ( rami kar ley. (aur pahley kar diye se) kuchh harj nahi. ibne-Amr kehtey hain (is din) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jis cheez ka bhi sawal hua, jo kisi ne aagey aur peechhey kar li thi. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ke ab kar ley aur kuchh harj nahi."
84,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ke (aakhirii) Haj mein kisi ne puchha ke maine rami karne (yani kankar phainkney) se pahley zabah kar liya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath se ishara kya (aur ( farmaya kuchh harj nahi. kisi ne kaha ke maine zabah se pahley halaq kara liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar se ishara farma diya ke kuchh harj nahi."
85,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (eik waqt aisa aayega ke jab ( ilm utha liya jaeyga jahaalat aur fitney phail jaeinge aur haraj badh jaeyga aap se puchha gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! haraj se kya murad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath ko harkat de kar farmaya us tarah, maano Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se qatl murad liya."
86,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aai , wo Namaz padh rahi thin, maine kaha ke logon ka kya haal hai? to unhon-ne aasman ki taraf ishara kya (yani suraj ko gehen laga hai) itney mein log (namaz ke liye) khadey ho gaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, Allah paak hai. maine kaha (kya ye gehen ( koi ( khas ( nishani hai? unhon-ne sar se ishara kya yani haan ! phir main ( bhi Namaz ke liye) khadi ho gaee. yahan tak ke mujhey ghash aaney laga, to main apne sar par pani dalney lagi phir (namaz ke baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah Taala ki tareef aur uski sifat bayan farmai, phir farmaya, jo cheez mujhey pahley dikhlai nahi gaee thi aaj wo sab us jagah maine dekh li, yahan tak ke jannat aur dozakh ko bhi dekh liya aur mujh par ye wahi ki gaee ke tum apni qabron mein aazmaey jaogey (misl) ya ( qurb (ka kon sa lafz Asma ne farmaya, mein nahi janti , Fatima kehti hain (yani ( fitna dajjal ki tarah (aazmaey jaaogey) kaha jaeyga (qabr ke andar ke) tum us aadmi ke barey mein kya jantey ho? to jo sahibe-emaan ya sahib yaqin hoga, kon sa lafz farmaya Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne, mujhey yad nahi. wo kahega wo Muhammad Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain, jo hamarey paas Allah ki hidayat aur daleelein lekar aaey to ham ne unko qabool kar liya aur unki pairwi ki wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. teen baar (usi tarah kahega) phir (is se) keh diya jaeyga ke aaraam se so ja beshak hamne jaan liya ke to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par yaqin rakhta tha aur bahar-haal munafiq ya shakki aadmii, mein nahi janti ke unmein se kon sa lafz Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, to wo (munaafiq ya shakki aadmii) kahega ke jo logon ko maine kehtey suna maine (bhi) wahi keh diya. (baqi mein kuchh nahi jaanta.)"
87,"mein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur logon ke darmyan tarjamani ke faraaiz anjam deta tha (eik martaba ( Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kon sa wafad hai? ya ye kon log hain? unhon-ne kaha ke Rabee khandan (ke log hain) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Mubarak ho qaum ko) aana (ya Mubarak ho us wafad ko (jo kabhi ( na ruswa ho na sharminda ho (iske baad) unhon-ne arz kya ke ham aik door daraaz koney se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey hain aur hamarey aur aap ke darmyan kuffaar Muzar ka ye qabila (padtaa) hai (iske khof ki wjah se) ham hurmat waley mahinon ke ilawa aur dinon mein nahi aa saktey. isliye hamein koi aisi (qat'ee) baat batla dijiye ke jiski ham apne peechhey reh janey waley logon ko khabar de dein. (aur ( uski wjah se ham jannat mein dakhil ho sakein. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein char baton ka hukm diya aur char se rok diyaa. awwal unhein hukm diya ke aik Allah par eman laaein. ( phir ( farmaya ke kya tum jantey ho ke aik Allah par eman laney ka kya matlab hai? unhon-ne arz kya, Allah aur uska rasool zyada jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (eik Allah par eman laney ka matlab ye hai ke) is baat ka iqrar karna ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain aur Namaz qaaim karnaa, zakat ada karna aur mahe-ramazan ke rozey rakhna aur ye ke tum maale-ghanimat se panchwan hissey ada karo aur char chizon se mana farmaya dubaa, hantam, aur muzaffat ke istemal se. aur (chauthii cheez ke barey mein) Shoba kehtey hain ke abu-Jamra kabhi-kabhi (Naqeer) kehtey they aur kabhi-kabhi (muqayyar). (iske baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un (baaton ko) yad rakho aur apne peechhey (rah jaaney) walon ko bhi unki khabar kar do."
88,"Aqba ne Abu-Ahaab bin azeez ki ladki se nikah kya to unke paas aik aurat aai aur kehney lagi ke maine Aqba ko aur jis se iska nikah hua hai, usko doodh pilaya hai. na to ney kabhi mujhey bataya hai. (ye sun kar) Aqba ne kaha, mujhey nahi malum ke tu ney mujhey doodh pilaya hai aur na to ney kabhi mujhey bataya hai. tab Aqba Sawar ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Madina Munawra hazir huey aur aap se iske mutaalliq malum kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kis tarah (tum us ladki se rishta rakhogey) halanke (iske mutaalliq ye ( kaha gaya tab Aqba bin-Haaris ne us ladki ko chhod diya aur usne doosra khawind kar liya."
89,"main aur mera aik Ansari padosi donon Madina k aas-paas ke aik gaaun bani Umayya bin Zaid mein rahtey they jo Madina ke) poorab ki taraf ( buland gaaun mein se hai. ham donon baari-baari Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat sharif mein hazir hua kartey they. aik din wo aata , aik din mein aataa. jis din mein aata us din ki wahi ki aur (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki farmooda) doosrey baton ki usko khabar de deta tha aur jab wo aata tha to wo bhi isi tarah karta. to aik din wo mera Ansari sathi apni baari ke roz haazire-khidmat hua (jab wapas aayaa) to usne mera darwaza bahut zor se khatkhataayaa aur (mere barey mein puchha ke) kya umr yahan hain? mein ghabraa kar uske paas aaya. wo kehney laga ke aik bada mamla pesh aa gaya hai. (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai) phir main (apni beti ( Hafsa ke paas gaya, wo ro rahi thi. maine poochha, kya tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talaaq de di hai? wo kehney lagi mein nahi jaantii. phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. maine khadey-khadey kaha ke kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi. (ye afawaah hai) tab maine (ta'jjub se) kaha ( Allahu-akbar ( Allah bahut bada hai."
90,"aik shakhs ( Hazam bin abi Kab ( ne ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa kar) arz kya. ya Rasulullah ! falan shakhs ( Muaz-bin-Jabal ( lambi Namaz padhatey hain isliye main ( jamat ki) Namaz mein Sharik nahi ho sakta (kyonke main din bhar oont charaney ki wjah se raat ko thak kar chaknaa- chor ho jata hun aur lamba qirat sunney ki taqat nahi rakhta ( ) Abu-Masood rawi kehtey hain) ke us din se zyada maine kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko waz (nasihat) ke doran itna ghazab naak nahi dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey logo ! tum ( aisi shiddat ikhtiyar karke logon ko Deen se) nafrat dilaane lagey ho. ( sun lo ( jo shakhs logon ko Namaz padhaaey to wo halki padhaaey , kyonke unmein bimar , kamzor aur haajat waley (sab hi qism ke log) hotey hain."
91,"aik shakhs ( Umer ya Bilal ( ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se padi hui cheez ke barey mein malum kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, uski bandhan pehchan ley ya farmaya ke iska bartan aur thaili ( pehchan ley ( phir aik saal tak uski shanaakht (ka elaan ( karao phir ( iska Malik na miley to (us se fayda uthao aur agar iska Malik aa jaey to usey saunp do. usne puchha ke achchha gum-shuda oont (ke barey mein) kya hukm hai? aapko is qadr ghussa aa gaya ke rukhsar Mubarak surkh ho gaey. ya rawi ne ye kaha ke aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya. (ye sun kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tujhey oont se kya waasta? iske sath khud uski mashk hai aur uske (paaun ke) sum hain. wo khud pani par pahunchega aur khud pi lega aur khud darakht par se charega. lihaza usey chhod do yahan tak ke uska Malik mil jaey. usne kaha ke achchha gum shuda bakri ke) barey mein) kya irshad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, wo teri hai ya terey bhai ki, warna bhediye ki) ghizaa ( hai."
92,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh aisi baatein malum ki gain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bura malum hua aur jab (is qism ke sawalat ki) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bahut zyadti ki gaee to aapko ghussa aa gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya ( achchha ab ( mujh se jo chaho poochho . to aik shakhs ne malum kya ke mera bap kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tera bap Huzafa hai. phir doosra aadmi khada hua aur us ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! mera bap kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tera bap Salim shabeeh ka aazad karda ghulam hai. aakhir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ke chehra Mubarak ka haal dekha to arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ham (un baton ke malum karne se jo aapko na-gawar hon ( Allah se tauba kartey hain."
93,"(eik din) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se nikley to Abdullah-bin Huzafa khadey ho kar poochhney lagey ke ya Rasulullah ! mera bap kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : huzaafa, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baar-baar farmaya ke mujh se poochho , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne 2 zaanu ho kar arz kya ke ham Allah ke rab honey par, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Nabi honey par razi hain (aur ye jumla ( teen martaba ( dohraya ( phir (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey."
94,jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) salam kartey to teen baar salam kartey aur jab koi baat irshad farmatey to usey teen baar dohraatey yahan tak ke khub samajh liya jata.
95,jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi baat irshad farmatey to usey teen baar dohraatey yahan tak ke khub samajh liya jata aur jab kuchh logon ke paas Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif latey aur unhein salam kartey to teen baar salam kartey.
96,aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham se peechhey reh gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey qareeb pahunchey. to Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho chuka tha ya tang ho gaya tha aur ham wuzu kar rahe they. ham apne pairon par pani ka hath pherney lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne buland awaz se farmaya ke aag ke azab se un eidiyon ki (jo khushk reh jaaein) kharabi hai. ye 2 martaba farmaya ya teen martaba.
97,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen shakhs hain jinke liye 2 guna ajr hai. aik wo jo ahle-kitab se ho aur apne Nabi par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman laey aur (doosrey ( wo ghulam jo apne aaqa aur Allah ( donon (ka haq ada karey aur) teesrey ( wo aadmi jiske paas koi londi ho. jis se shab-baashii (ham-bistari) karta hai aur usey tarbiyat de to achi tarbiyat de, taleem de to umda taleem de, phir usey aazad karke usse nikah kar ley, to uske liye 2 guna ajr hai. phir Aamir ne (Saaleh-bin-Hayyaan se) kaha ke ham ne ye hadis tumhen baghair ujrat ke suna di hai) warna (us se kam hadis ke liye Madina tak ka safar kya jata tha."
98,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par gawahi deta hun, ya Ata ne kaha ke main Ibne-Abbas par gawahi deta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik martaba eid ke mauqe par mardon ki safon mein se) nikley aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) they. aapko khayal hua ke aurton ko) khutba achi tarah) nahi sunai diya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein alehda nasihat farmai aur sadqey ka hukm diya (ye waz (nasihat) sun kar) koi aurat baali (aur koi aurat) anguthi dalney lagi aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) apne kapdey ke daman mein (ye cheezein) leney lagey. us hadis ko Ismail bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Ata se ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par gawahi deta hun (is mein shak nahi hai). imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ki gharaz ye hai ke aglaa baab aam logon se mutaalliq tha aur ye Hakim aur imam se mutaalliq hai ke wo bhi aurton ko waz (nasihat) sunaaiye."
99,"unhon-ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah! qiyamat ke din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shafaat se sabse zyada khush-naseebi kisey milegi? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey yaqin tha ke tum se pahley koi iske barey mein mujh se malum nahi karega. kyonke maine hadis ke mutaalliq tumhari hirs dekh li thi. suno! qiyamat mein sabse zyada faizyaab meri shafaat se wo shakhs hoga, jo sachey dil se ya sachey ji se ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahega."
100,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke Allah ilm ko is tarah nahi utha lega ke usko bandon se chheen ley. balke wo ( pukhta kaar ( ulma ko maut de kar ilm ko uthaaeyga . yahan tak ke jab koi aalim baqi nahi rahega to log jaahilon ko sardaar bana lengey , unse sawalat kiye jaeinge aur wo baghair ilm ke jawab dengey. isliye khud bhi gumrah hongey aur logon ko bhi gumrah karengey. farbarii ne kaha ham se Abbas ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Quteba ne, kaha ham se Jarir ne, unhon-ne Hisham se manind (tarah) us hadis ke."
101,"aurton ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se fayda uthaney mein) mard ham se aagey badh gaey hain, isliye aap apni taraf se hamarey ( waz (nasihat) ke) liye ( bhi) koi din khas farma dein. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse aik din ka wada farma liya. us din aurton se aap ne mulaqat ki aur unhein waz (nasihat) farmaya aur) munasib ( ehkaam sunaaiye jo kuchh Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha usmein ye baat bhi thi ke jo koi aurat tum mein se (apne ( teen ( ladkey ( aagey bhej degi to wo uske liye dozakh se panah bin jaengey. is par aik aurat ne kaha, agar 2 (bachchey bhej de) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan ! aur 2 (ka bhi ye hukm hai)."
102,unhon-ne farmaya ke aisey teen (bachchey) jo abhi baligh umr ko na pahunchey hun.
103,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) jab koi aisi baatein sunnatein jis ko samajh na paatiin to dobara usko malum kartin taake samajh lein. chunanche (eik martaba ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis se hisab liya gaya usey azab kya jaeyga Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke (ye sun kar) maine kaha ke kya Allah ne ye nahi farmaya ke an-qareeb usse aasan hisab liya jaaeyga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye sirf (Allah ke darbar mein) peshii ka zikr hai. lekin jiske hisab mein jaanch-padtaal ki gaee (samjho) wo ghaarat ho gaya.
104,"unhon-ne Amr bin Saeed (Madina ke governor ( se jab wo Makka main ( ibne-Zubair se ladney ke liye) faujein bhej rahe they kaha ke aey ameer ! mujhey aap ijazat dein to main wo hadis aap se bayan kar dun, jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke doosrey din irshad farmai thi, us ( hadis) ko mere donon kanon ne suna aur mere dil ne usey yad rakha hai aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye hadis farma rahe they, to meri aankhen Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (pahley ( Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya ke Makka ko Allah ne haram kya hai, aadmiyon ne haram nahi kya. to ( sun lo (ke kisi shakhs ke liye jo Allah par aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhta ho jaaiz nahi hai ke Makka mein khoon-rezii karey, ya iska koi peid kaatey , phir agar koi Allah ke rasool (ke ladney ( ki wjah se iska jawaz nikaley to us se keh do Allah ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye ijazat di thi, tumharey liye nahi di aur mujhey bhi din ke kuchh lamhon ke liye ijazat mili thi. aaj uski hurmat lot aaii, jaisi kal thi aur hazir ghayab ko (ye baat ( pahuncha de. (ye hadis sunney ke baad rawi hadis) abu-Shuraih se puchha gaya ke (aap ki ye baat sun kar) Amr ne kya jawab diya ? kaha yun ke aey ( abu-Shuraih ! ( hadis ko main tum se zyada janta hun. magar haram (Makka) kisi khataakaar ko ya khoon karke aur fitna phaila kar bhag aaney waley ko panah nahi detaa."
105,"aik martaba Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( yun ( farmaya, tumharey khoon aur tumharey maal , Muhammad kehtey hain ke mere khayal mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( وأعراضكم (ka lafz bhi farmaya, (yani (aur tumhari aabrooyein tum par haram hain. jis tarah tumharey aaj ke din ki hurmat tumharey us mahiney mein. sun lo! ye khabar hazir ghayab ko pahuncha de. aur Muhammad ( rawi hadis) kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sach farmaya, ( phir ( dobara farmaya ke kya maine ( Allah ka ye hukm ( tumhen nahi pahuncha diya."
106,maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujh par jhoot mat bolo. kyonke jo mujh par jhoot baandhey wo dozakh mein dakhil ho.
107,"maine kabhi aap se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadison nahi suniin. jaisa ke fulaan, falan bayan karte hain, kaha, main kabhi aap se alag thalag nahi raha lekin maine aapko ye bhi farmatey huey suna hai ke jo shakhs mujh par jhoot baandhega wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley."
108,mujhey bahut si hadisein bayan karne se ye baat rokti hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs mujh par jaan-bojh kar jhoot baandhey to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.
109,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke jo shakhs mere naam se wo baat bayan kare jo maine nahi kahi to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.
110,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke (apni aulad (ka mere naam ke uper naam rakho. magar meri kunniyat ikhtiyar na karo aur jis shakhs ne mujhey khuwab mein dekha to bila shubah usne mujhey dekha. kyonke shaitan meri sura mein nahi aa sakta aur jo shakhs mujh par jaan-bojh kar jhoot boley wo dozakh mein apna thikana talash kare.
111,"maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya aap ke paas koi (aur bhi) kitab hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi, magar Allah ki kitab Quran hai ya phir faham aur samajh hai jo wo aik musalman ko ata karta hai. ya phir jo kuchh us saheefey mein hai. maine poochha, us saheefey mein kya hai? unhon-ne farmaya, diyat aur qaidiyon ki rihaaii ka bayan hai aur ye hukm ke muslmaan, kaafir ke badley qatl na kya jaey."
112,"qabila khuza'aa (ke kisi shakhs) ne banu- Leis ke kisi aadmi ko apne kisi maqtool ke badley mein mar diya tha, ye fateh Makka waley saal ki baat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye khabar di gaee, aap ne apni ontni par Sawar ho kar khutba padha aur farmaya ke Allah ne Makka se qatl ya haathii ko rok liya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain us lafz ko shak ke sath samjho , aisa hi abu-Nueim wghaira ne ( القتل (aur ( feel ( kaha hai. unke ilawa doosrey log ( feel ( kehtey hain. ( phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke Allah ne un par apne rasool aur musalman ko ghalib kar diya aur samajh lo ke wo (Makka) kisi ke liye halal nahi hua. na mujh se pahley aur na ( aainda ( kabhi hoga aur mere liye bhi sirf din ke thodey se hisse ke liye halal kar diya gaya tha. sun lo ke wo us waqt haram hai. na iska koi kaantaa todaa jaey, na iske darakht kaatey jayen aur uski girii-padii cheezein bhi wahi uthaey jiska irada ye ho ke wo us cheez ka Taaruf : kara dega. to agar koi shakhs maara jaey to (iske azeezon ko) ikhtiyar hai 2 baton ka, ya diyat lein ya badla. itney mein aik yamnii aadmi ( Abu-Shah naamii) aaya aur kehney laga (ye masayel ( mere liye likhwaa dijiye. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Fulaan ke liye (ye masayel ( likh do. to aik qureshi shakhs ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! magar izkhir (yani izkhir kaatney ki ijazat de diijiye) kyonke usey ham gharon ki chhaton par daltey hain. (ya mitti mila kar) aur apni qabron mein bhi daltey hain (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) haan ( magar izkhir, magar izkhir."
113,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa mujh se zyada koi hadis bayan karne wala nahi tha. magar wo likh liya kartey they aur main likhtaa nahi tha. dusri sanad se Mamar ne Wahab-bin-Munabba ki mutabiat (pairavi) ki, wo Hammam se riwayat kartey hain, wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se."
114,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein shiddat ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas saamaane-kitaabat lao taake tumharey liye aik tahreer likh dun, taake baad main tum gumrah na ho sako, is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (logon se) kaha ke us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par takleef ka ghalba hai aur hamarey paas Allah ki kitab Quran maujood hai jo hamein (hidaayat ke liye) kafi hai. is par logon ki raey mukhtalif ho gaee aur shor w ghul zyada honey laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere paas se uth khadey ho, mere paas jhagadnaa theek nahi, is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey huey nikal aaey ke beshak museebat badi sakht museebat hai (wo cheez jo) hamarey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur aap ki tahreer ke darmyan haail ho gaee."
115,aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bedaar hotey hi farmaya ke Subhan-Allah ! aaj ki raat kis qadr fitney utaarey gaey hain aur kitney hi khazaaney bhi kholey gaey hain. in hujre waaliyon ko jagaao. kyonke bahut si auratein (jo ( duniya main ( baareek ( kapda pahnney wali hain wo aakhirat mein nangii hongii.
116,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aakhir umr mein (eik baar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein isha ki Namaz padhai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to khadey ho gaey aur farmaya ke tumhari aaj ki raat wo hai ke us raat se 100 baras ke aakhir tak koi shakhs jo zameen par hai wo baqi nahi rahega.
117,"aik raat maine apni khala memoona-bint-al-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) bevi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas guzari aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is din) unki raat mein un hi ke ghar they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz masjid mein padhi. phir ghar tashrif laey aur char rakaat (namaz nafl) padh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey, phir uthey aur farmaya ke (abhii tak ye) ladka so raha hai ya usi jaisa lafz farmaya, phir aap (namaz padhney) khadey ho gaey aur main (bhi wuzu karke) aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey daain taraf ( khada ( kar liya, tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne panch rakaat padhin. phir 2 padhin, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey. yahan tak ke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kharraatey ki awaz suni, phir aap khadey ho kar Namaz ke liye ( bahar ( tashrif ley aaey."
118,"log kehtey hain ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bahut hadisein bayan kartey hain aur (mein kehta hon) ke Quran mein 2 aayatein na hotiin to main koi hadis bayan na karta. phir ye aayat padhi, (jiska tarjama ye hai) ke jo log Allah ki nazil ki hui daleelon aur aayaton ko chhipaatey hain (aakhir aayat) ( رحيم‏ ( tak. (waaqia ye hai ke) hamarey muhajireen bhai to bazar ki khareed w farokht mein lagey rahtey they aur Ansar bhai apni jaaydaadon mein mashghool rahtey aur abu-Huraira, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ji bhar kar rehta (taake aapki dosti mein pet bharne se bhi be-fikrii rahe (aur (un majlison mein) hazir rehta jin ( majlison ( mein doosrey hazir na hotey aur wo ( baatein ( mehfooz rakhta jo doosrey mehfooz nahi rakh saktey they."
119,"maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah! main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bahut baatein sunta hon, magar bhool jata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya apni chadar phailaao, maine apni chadar phailaaii , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon ki chullu banai aur (meri chadar mein daal di) farmaya ke) chadar ko) lapet lo. maine chadar ko (apne badan par) lapet liya, phir (iske baad) mein koi cheez nahi bhoolaa. ham se Ibrahim bin al-Munzir ne bayan kya, unse ibne- abii-Fidya ne isi tarah bayan kya ke) yun ( farmaya ke apne hath se aik chullu us ( chadar ( mein daal di."
120,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ilm ke) 2 bartan yad kar liye hain, aik ko maine phaila diya hai aur doosra bartan agar main phailaaun to mera ye narkharaa kaat diya jaey. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke (aam taur se) murad wo narkharaa hai jisse khana utartaa hai."
121,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse Hijjatul-wada mein farmaya ke logon ko bilkul khamosh kar do (taake wo khub sun lein) phir farmaya, logo! mere baad phir kaafir mat bin jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago."
122,"Nauf Bakaalii ka ye khayal hai ke Musa (Alaihissalam) (jo khizr (Alaihissalam) ke paas gaey they wo ( Musa Bani-Israeel waley nahi they balke doosrey Musa they, (ye sun kar) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke Allah ke dushman ne jhoot kaha hai. ham se Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya ke (eik roz ( Musa (Alaihissalam) ne khadey ho kar Bani-Israeel mein khutba diya, to aap se puchha gaya ke logon mein sabse zyada saahibe-ilm kon hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke main hun. us wjah se Allah ka ghussa un par hua ke unhon-ne ilm ko Allah ke hawale kyon na kar diya. tab Allah ne unki taraf wahi bheji ke mere bandon mein se aik banda daryaon ke sangam par hai. ( jahan Faaris aur Rome (mojooda Itly) ke samandar miltey hain) wo tujh se zyada aalim hai, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha aey parwardigar ! meri unse mulaqat kaisey ho? hukm hua ke aik machhli zanbeel mein rakh lo, phir jahan tum us machhli ko gum kar doge to wo banda tumhen ( wahin ( milega. tab Musa (Alaihissalam) chaley aur sath apne khaadim Yoosha-bin-Noon ko ley liya aur unhon-ne zanbeel mein machhli rakh li, jab (eik ( patthar ke paas pahunchey, donon apne sar is par rakh kar so gaey aur machhli zanbeel se nikal kar dariya main apni raah banati chali gaee aur ye baat Musa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi ke liye behad tajjub ki thi, phir donon baqi raat aur din mein (jitna waqt baqi tha) chaltey rahe, jab subah hui Musa (Alaihissalam) ne khaadim se kaha, hamara naashta laao, us safar mein ham ne ( kafi ( takleef uthai hai aur Musa (Alaihissalam) bilkul nahi thakey they, magar jab us jagah se aagey nikal gaey, jahan tak unhein janey ka hukm mila tha, tab unke khaadim ne kaha, kya aap ne dekha tha ke jab ham Sakhra ke paas thahrey they, to main machhli ka zikr bhool gaya, ( baqaul kuchh Sakhra ke nichey aab hayaat tha, wo us machhli par padaa , aur wo zinda ho kar Allah ki qudrat se dariya mein chal di ( (ye sun kar) Musa (Alaihissalam) boley ke ye hi wo jagah hai jiski hamein talash thi, to wo pichhley paon wapas ho gaey, jab patthar tak pahunchey to dekha ke aik shakhs kapda odhey huey ( maujood hai) Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unhein salam kya, khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke tumhari sar zameen mein salam kahan ? phir Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke main Musa ( (Alaihissalam) ( hun. khizr boley ke Bani-Israeel ke Musa ? unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan! phir kaha kya main aap ke sath chal sakta hon, taake aap mujhey hidayat ki wo baatein batlaayein jo Allah ne khas aap hi ko sikhlaaii hain. khizr (Alaihissalam) boley ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar sakogey. aey Moosaa! mujhey Allah ne aisa ilm diya hai jisey tum nahi jantey aur tum ko jo ilm diya hai usey mein nahi janta. (is par) Musa ne kaha ke Allah ne chaha to aap mujhey saabir paogey aur main kisi baat mein aap ki nafarmani nahi karunga. phir donon dariya ke kinarey kinaarey paidal chaley, unke paas koi kashtii na thi ke aik kashtii unke samney se guzri , to kashtii waalon se unhon-ne kaha ke hamein bitha lo. khizr (Alaihissalam) ko unhon-ne pehchan liya aur baghair kiraaya ke sawar kar liya, itney mein aik chidiyaa aai aur kashtii ke kinarey par baith gaee, phir samandar mein usne aik ya 2 chonchein maarein (usey dekh kar) khizr (Alaihissalam) boley ke aey Moosaa! mere aur tumharey ilm ne Allah ke ilm mein se itna hi kam kya hoga jitna us chidiyaa ne samandar (ke pani ( se phir khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kashtii ke takhton mein se aik takhta nikal daalaa, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke un logon ne to hamein kiraaya liye baghair ( muft mein) sawar kya aur aap ne unki kashtii (ki lakdii) ukhaad dali taake ye doob jaaein, khizr (Alaihissalam) boley ke kya maine nahi kaha tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar sakogey ? (us par) Musa (Alaihissalam) ne jawab diya ke bhool par meri giraft na karo. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne bhool kar ye pahlaa aetraz kya tha. phir donon chaley (kashtii se utar kar) aik ladka bachchon ke sath khel raha tha, khizr (Alaihissalam) ne uper se iska sar pakad kar hath se usey alag kar diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) bol padey ke aap ne aik be-gunaah bachchey ko baghair kisi jaani haq ke mar daala ( ghazab ho gaya) khizr (Alaihissalam) boley ke maine tum se nahi kaha tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar sakogey . ibne-Uena kehtey hain ke us kalam mein pahley se zyada takeed hai (kyonke pahley kalam mein lafz لک nahi kaha tha, usmein لک zayed kya, jis se takeed zahir hai) phir donon chaltey rahe. yahan tak ke aik gaaun walon ke paas aaey, unse khana lena chaha . unhon-ne khana khilaaney se inkar kar diya. unhon-ne wahin dekha ke aik diwar usi gaaun mein girney ke qareeb thi. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apne hath ke ishaarey se usey seedha kar diya. Musa bol uthey ke agar aap chahtey to ( gaaun walon se) us kaam ki mazdoorii le saktey they. khizr ne kaha ke (bas ab) ham aur tum mein judai ka waqt aa gaya hai. janab mahboob kibriyaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey hain ke Allah Musa par raham karey, hamari tamanna thi ke Musa kuchh der aur sabr kartey to mazeed waaqiaat un donon ke bayan kiye jatey (aur hamarey samney roshni mein aatey, magar Musa (Alaihissalam) ki ujlat ne us ilme-ladunnii (ilme-ilaahii) ke silsile ko jald hi khatm kara diyaa) Muhammad-bin Yusuf kehtey hain ke ham se Ali-bin-Khashram ne ye hadis bayan ki, unse Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne poori ki poori bayan ki."
123,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat aqdas mein hazir hua aur usne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki raah mein ladai ki kya sura hai? kyonke ham mein se koi ghusse ki wjah se aur koi ghairat ki wjah se jang karta hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf sar uthaayaa, aur sar isi liye uthaya ke poochhney wala khada hua tha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo Allah ke kalime ko sr-buland karne ke liye ladey, wo Allah ki raah main ( ladtaa ( hai."
124,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rami jimaar ke waqt dekha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ja raha tha to aik shakhs ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! maine rami se qabl qurbani kar li ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ab ( rami kar lo kuchh harj nahi hua. doosrey ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! maine qurbani se pahley sar mundaa liya ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ab ( qurbani kar lo kuchh harj nahi. (is waqt) jis cheez ke barey mein jo aagey peechhey ho gaee thi, aap se puchha gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye hi jawab diya ( ab ( kar lo kuchh harj nahi."
125,"(eik martaba ( main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke khandraat mein chal raha tha aur aap khajoor ki chhadi par sahara de kar chal rahe they, to kuchh yahudiyon ka (udhar se) guzar hua, unmein se aik ne doosrey se kaha ke aap se Rooh ke barey mein kuchh poochho, unmein se kisi ne kaha mat poochho, aisa na ho ke wo koi aisi baat keh dein jo tumhen na-gawar ho (magar) unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke ham zaroor poochhenge, phir aik shakhs ne khade hokar kaha, aey abul-Qaasim! Rooh kya cheez hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khamoshi ikhtiyar farmai, maine (dil mein) kaha ke aap par wahi aa rahi hai. isliye main khada ho gaya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (wo kaifiyat ( door ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Quran ki ye aayat jo us waqt nazil hui thi) tilawat farmai '' (aey Nabi ! ( tum se ye log Rooh ke barey mein poochh rahe hain. keh do ke Rooh mere rab ke hukm se hai. aur tumhen ilm ka bahut thoda hissey diya gaya hai.'' (is liye tum Rooh ki haqiqat nahi samajh saktey ( Aamash kehtey hain ke hamari qirat main ( وما اوتوا ( hai. ( ‏‏‏‏وما اوتيتم ( Mina ( nahi."
126,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) tum se bahut baatein chipa kar kehti thin, to kya tum se Kaba ke barey mein bhi kuchh bayan kya, maine kaha ( haan ( mujh se unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik martaba ( irshad farmaya tha ke aey Aaisha ! agar teri qaum ( daure-jaahiliyat ke saath) qareeb na hoti ( balke puraanii ho gaee hoti ( ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha yani zamana kufr ke sath ( qareeb na hoti ( to main Kaba ko tod deta aur uske liye 2 darwazey bana deta. aik darwazey se log dakhil hotey aur doosrey darwazey se bahar nikaltey , ( baad mein) ibne-Zubair ne ye kaam kya."
127,"mazmoon hadis ( حدثوا Naas بما يعرفون ( الخ bayan kya, ( tarjama guzar chuka hai.)"
128,"(eik martaba ( Muaz-bin-Jabal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey sawari par Sawar they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya, hazir hun ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dobara ( farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya, hazir hun aey Allah ke rasool! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (teesrii baar) farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya, hazir hun, aey Allah ke rasool , teen baar aisa hua. (iske baad) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs sachey dil se is baat ki gawahi de ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi hai aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain, Allah Taala usko (dozakh ki) aag par haram kar deta hai. maine kaha ya Rasulullah! kya is baat se logon ko ba-khabar na kar dun taake wo khush ho jayen ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (agar tum ye khabar sunaaogey) to log is par bharosa kar baithein gey (aur amal chhod denge) Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne intiqal ke waqt ye hadis us khayal se bayan farma di ke kahin hadeese-rasool chhipaaney ke gunah par unse aakhirat mein poochh-gachch na ho."
129,"mujh se bayan kya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik roz Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke jo shakhs Allah se us kaifiyat ke sath mulaqat karey ke usne Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na kya ho, wo ( yaqinan ( jannat mein dakhil hoga, Muaz boley, ya Rasulullah ! kya main is baat ki logon ko bashaarat na suna dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi, mujhey khof hai ke log is par bharosa kar baithenge."
130,"Umme-Sulaim ( naam ke aik aurat ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat aqdas mein hazir huin aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala haq baat bayan karne se nahi sharmaataa (is liye mein poochhtii hon ke) kya ehtilam se aurat par bhi ghusl zaroori hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) haan ( jab aurat pani dekh ley. (yani kapdey wghaira par mani ka asar malum ho ( to (ye sun kar) Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne ( sharm ki wjah se) apna chehra chipa liya aur kaha, ya Rasulullah ! kya aurat ko bhi ehtilam hota hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, haan ! terey hath khaak aalud hon, phir kyon iska bachcha uski sura ke mushabeh (similar) hota hai (yani yahi iske ehtilam ka saboot hai)."
131,"darakhton mein se aik darakht (aisa) hai, jiske patey (kabhii) nahi jhadtey aur uski misal musalman jaisi hai. mujhey batlao wo kya ( darakht ( hai? to log janglii darakhton (ki soch ( mein pad gaey aur mere dil mein aaya (ke mein batla dun (ke wo khajoor (ka peid ( hai, Abdullah kehtey hain ke phir mujhey sharm aa gaee (aur mein chup hi raha ( tab logon ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! aap hi ( khud ( iske baare mein batlaaiye , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, wo khajoor hai. Abdullah kehtey hain ke mere ji mein jo baat thi wo maine apne walid ( umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ko batlaaii , wo kehney lagey ke agar to (us waqt) keh deta to mere liye aisey-aisey qeemtii sarmaaye se zyada mahboob hota."
132,"mein aisa shakhs tha jisey Jiryaan mazi ki shikayat thi, to maine (apne shagird ( Miqdad ko hukm diya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum karein. to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us barey mein poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us ( marz ( mein ghusl nahi hai) haan ( wuzu farz hai."
133,"(eik martaba ( aik aadmi ne masjid mein khadey ho kar arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! aap hamein kis jagah se ehram baandhney ka hukm detey hain? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Madina waley zul-Hulaifa se ehram baandhein , aur ahale-Shaam (Syria) Johfa se aur Najad waley Qarnul-Manaazil se. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, ke logon ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Yaman waley Yalamlam se ehram baandhein aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke mujhey ye (aakhirii jumla) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yad nahi."
134,aik shakhs ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ehram baandhney waley ko kya pahannaa chahiye ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke na qamees pahney na saafa baandhey aur na paa-jaama aur na koi sarposh odhey aur na koi zafran aur waras se ranga hua kapda pahney aur agar jootey na milein to mozey pahan ley aur unhein (is tarah) kaat de ke takhnon se nichey ho jaaein.
